{% comment %}
  Free Gift Engine — section app block. RESERVED FOR PHASE 5b-2 (the perception UI: progress widget,
  "Choose your free gift" chooser, "Add my free gift" decline checkbox). It renders nothing in 5b-1
  and does NOT load the controller.

  The engine (controller script + config) is delivered by the app EMBED (free-gift-embed.liquid),
  enabled under Theme settings -> App embeds — it loads site-wide and does not require a section that
  accepts app blocks. If this theme's cart sections don't offer app blocks, that's fine: 5b-1 needs
  only the embed; 5b-2 will decide where the visible UI mounts.
{% endcomment %}

<div data-fge-ui-mount hidden></div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Free Gift",
  "target": "section",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
